## Current state

- Popup exposes 4 mode buttons (`exact`, `ai-refine`, `extended-refine`, `extended-handoff`) + stop / copy-latest / copy-debug-log + settings.
- Two backend paths: `runStandardRefinementJob` (1 call) and `runExtendedRefinement` (~17 calls, persona chain). `EXTENDED_PIPELINES.refinement` / `.handoff` already configure extended type as data.
- Short path uses the single active prompt; it has no Task/Handoff concept yet.

